  "commit_message": "Wasm R2R: push this before retbuf in InterpToR2R thunk args (#129356)\n\nThe thunk pushed retbuf before this, but the JIT (lvaInitArgs) and\nWasmR2RToInterpreterThunk both expect (, [this], [retbuf], ...). Swap\nthe two if-blocks so interp -> R2R calls match. Fixes #129347 (NRE /\npMT->Validate assert for Synchronized + struct return).",
